WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.082 --> 00:00:17.165
I come to you today to speak of liars,

00:00:17.189 --> 00:00:18.612
lawsuits

00:00:18.636 --> 00:00:19.976
and laughter.

00:00:20.910 --> 00:00:24.020
The first time I heard
about Holocaust denial,

00:00:24.044 --> 00:00:25.346
I laughed.

00:00:25.970 --> 00:00:27.722
Holocaust denial?

00:00:28.187 --> 00:00:31.617
The Holocaust which has
the dubious distinction

00:00:31.641 --> 00:00:36.136
of being the best-documented
genocide in the world?

00:00:37.046 --> 00:00:39.072
Who could believe it didn't happen?

00:00:40.106 --> 00:00:41.453
Think about it.

00:00:42.257 --> 00:00:44.538
For deniers to be right,

00:00:44.562 --> 00:00:46.458
who would have to be wrong?

00:00:47.011 --> 00:00:49.777
Well, first of all, the victims --

00:00:49.801 --> 00:00:54.518
the survivors who have told us
their harrowing stories.

00:00:55.721 --> 00:00:58.035
Who else would have to be wrong?

00:00:58.059 --> 00:01:00.012
The bystanders.

00:01:00.036 --> 00:01:04.014
The people who lived in the myriads
of towns and villages and cities

00:01:04.038 --> 00:01:06.010
on the Eastern front,

00:01:06.034 --> 00:01:08.476
who watched their neighbors
be rounded up --

00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:11.713
men, women, children, young, old --

00:01:11.737 --> 00:01:14.457
and be marched
to the outskirts of the town

00:01:14.481 --> 00:01:17.473
to be shot and left dead in ditches.

00:01:17.985 --> 00:01:19.315
Or the Poles,

00:01:19.339 --> 00:01:24.020
who lived in towns and villages
around the death camps,

00:01:24.044 --> 00:01:26.420
who watched day after day

00:01:26.444 --> 00:01:29.186
as the trains went in filled with people

00:01:29.210 --> 00:01:30.733
and came out empty.

00:01:31.787 --> 00:01:35.420
But above all, who would have to be wrong?

00:01:36.005 --> 00:01:37.469
The perpetrators.

00:01:38.112 --> 00:01:41.018
The people who say, "We did it.

00:01:41.479 --> 00:01:43.003
I did it."

00:01:43.027 --> 00:01:45.176
Now, maybe they add a caveat.

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:49.624
They say, "I didn't have a choice;
I was forced to do it."

00:01:50.104 --> 00:01:52.773
But nonetheless, they say, "I did it."

00:01:53.938 --> 00:01:55.489
Think about it.

00:01:55.513 --> 00:02:01.452
In not one war crimes trial
since the end of World War II

00:02:01.476 --> 00:02:08.112
has a perpetrator of any nationality
ever said, "It didn't happen."

00:02:09.078 --> 00:02:13.660
Again, they may have said, "I was forced,"
but never that it didn't happen.

00:02:13.684 --> 00:02:15.158
Having thought that through,

00:02:15.182 --> 00:02:19.133
I decided denial was not
going to be on my agenda;

00:02:19.157 --> 00:02:22.865
I had bigger things to worry about,
to write about, to research,

00:02:22.889 --> 00:02:24.203
and I moved on.

00:02:24.911 --> 00:02:27.730
Fast-forward a little over a decade,

00:02:27.754 --> 00:02:29.566
and two senior scholars --

00:02:29.590 --> 00:02:32.748
two of the most prominent historians
of the Holocaust --

00:02:32.772 --> 00:02:34.029
approached me and said,

00:02:34.053 --> 00:02:35.842
"Deborah, let's have coffee.

00:02:35.866 --> 00:02:39.463
We have a research idea
that we think is perfect for you."

00:02:39.487 --> 00:02:43.320
Intrigued and flattered
that they came to me with an idea

00:02:43.344 --> 00:02:44.921
and thought me worthy of it,

00:02:44.945 --> 00:02:47.041
I asked, "What is it?"

00:02:47.665 --> 00:02:50.654
And they said, "Holocaust denial."

00:02:51.353 --> 00:02:53.848
And for the second time, I laughed.

00:02:54.336 --> 00:02:56.260
Holocaust denial?

00:02:56.284 --> 00:02:58.270
The Flat Earth folks?

00:02:58.294 --> 00:03:00.431
The Elvis-is-alive people?

00:03:00.455 --> 00:03:02.643
I should study them?

00:03:03.326 --> 00:03:04.643
And these two guys said,

00:03:04.667 --> 00:03:06.600
"Yeah, we're intrigued.

00:03:07.012 --> 00:03:08.584
What are they about?

00:03:08.608 --> 00:03:10.358
What's their objective?

00:03:10.382 --> 00:03:14.036
How do they manage to get people
to believe what they say?"

00:03:14.756 --> 00:03:18.284
So thinking, if they thought
it was worthwhile,

00:03:18.308 --> 00:03:21.682
I would take a momentary diversion --

00:03:21.706 --> 00:03:24.644
maybe a year, maybe two,
three, maybe even four --

00:03:24.668 --> 00:03:26.913
in academic terms, that's momentary.

00:03:26.937 --> 00:03:28.079
(Laughter)

00:03:28.103 --> 00:03:30.490
We work very slowly.

00:03:30.514 --> 00:03:32.086
(Laughter)

00:03:32.110 --> 00:03:33.912
And I would look at them.

00:03:33.936 --> 00:03:35.091
So I did.

00:03:35.115 --> 00:03:37.954
I did my research, and I came up
with a number of things,

00:03:37.978 --> 00:03:40.571
two of which I'd like to share
with you today.

00:03:40.595 --> 00:03:41.928
One:

00:03:41.952 --> 00:03:46.909
deniers are wolves in sheep's clothing.

00:03:47.712 --> 00:03:50.677
They are the same: Nazis, neo-Nazis --

00:03:50.701 --> 00:03:53.928
you can decide whether you want
to put a "neo" there or not.

00:03:54.786 --> 00:03:57.119
But when I looked at them,

00:03:57.143 --> 00:04:01.869
I didn't see any SS-like uniforms,

00:04:01.893 --> 00:04:05.044
swastika-like symbols on the wall,

00:04:05.068 --> 00:04:07.125
Sieg Heil salutes --

00:04:07.149 --> 00:04:08.693
none of that.

00:04:08.717 --> 00:04:11.587
What I found instead

00:04:11.611 --> 00:04:16.226
were people parading
as respectable academics.

00:04:16.916 --> 00:04:18.137
What did they have?

00:04:18.161 --> 00:04:19.859
They had an institute.

00:04:19.883 --> 00:04:23.727
An "Institute for Historical Review."

00:04:24.392 --> 00:04:26.946
They had a journal -- a slick journal --

00:04:26.970 --> 00:04:29.924
a "Journal of Historical Review."

00:04:30.398 --> 00:04:33.104
One filled with papers --

00:04:33.128 --> 00:04:35.172
footnote-laden papers.

00:04:35.923 --> 00:04:37.863
And they had a new name.

00:04:38.500 --> 00:04:40.668
Not neo-Nazis,

00:04:40.692 --> 00:04:43.182
not anti-Semites --

00:04:43.206 --> 00:04:44.464
revisionists.

00:04:44.991 --> 00:04:47.206
They said, "We are revisionists.

00:04:47.230 --> 00:04:49.913
We are out to do one thing:

00:04:49.937 --> 00:04:53.497
to revise mistakes in history."

00:04:54.369 --> 00:04:59.779
But all you had to do was go
one inch below the surface,

00:04:59.803 --> 00:05:01.710
and what did you find there?

00:05:01.734 --> 00:05:04.224
The same adulation of Hitler,

00:05:04.248 --> 00:05:06.123
praise of the Third Reich,

00:05:06.147 --> 00:05:09.089
anti-Semitism, racism, prejudice.

00:05:09.904 --> 00:05:12.350
This is what intrigued me.

00:05:12.374 --> 00:05:19.371
It was anti-Semitism, racism, prejudice,
parading as rational discourse.

00:05:20.730 --> 00:05:22.317
The other thing I found --

00:05:22.341 --> 00:05:26.086
many of us have been taught to think
there are facts and there are opinions --

00:05:26.110 --> 00:05:27.566
after studying deniers,

00:05:27.590 --> 00:05:28.926
I think differently.

00:05:29.438 --> 00:05:31.086
There are facts,

00:05:31.110 --> 00:05:32.824
there are opinions,

00:05:32.848 --> 00:05:34.460
and there are lies.

00:05:35.149 --> 00:05:39.575
And what deniers want to do
is take their lies,

00:05:40.565 --> 00:05:42.197
dress them up as opinions --

00:05:42.221 --> 00:05:44.211
maybe edgy opinions,

00:05:44.235 --> 00:05:46.944
maybe sort of out-of-the-box opinions --

00:05:46.968 --> 00:05:48.352
but then if they're opinions,

00:05:48.376 --> 00:05:50.508
they should be part of the conversation.

00:05:50.532 --> 00:05:53.925
And then they encroach on the facts.

00:05:55.305 --> 00:05:56.868
I published my work --

00:05:56.892 --> 00:05:58.066
the book was published,

00:05:58.090 --> 00:06:01.492
"Denying the Holocaust: The Growing
Assault on Truth and Memory,"

00:06:01.516 --> 00:06:03.472
it came out in many different countries,

00:06:03.496 --> 00:06:05.656
including here in Penguin UK,

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:09.110
and I was done with those folks
and ready to move on.

00:06:10.163 --> 00:06:13.871
Then came the letter from Penguin UK.

00:06:14.434 --> 00:06:17.202
And for the third time, I laughed ...

00:06:19.088 --> 00:06:20.328
mistakenly.

00:06:20.972 --> 00:06:22.702
I opened the letter,

00:06:22.726 --> 00:06:28.614
and it informed me that David Irving
was bringing a libel suit against me

00:06:28.638 --> 00:06:30.235
in the United Kingdom

00:06:30.259 --> 00:06:33.295
for calling him a Holocaust denier.

00:06:33.953 --> 00:06:35.887
David Irving suing me?

00:06:35.911 --> 00:06:37.115
Who was David Irving?

00:06:37.139 --> 00:06:39.746
David Irving was a writer
of historical works,

00:06:39.770 --> 00:06:41.793
most of them about World War II,

00:06:41.817 --> 00:06:45.036
and virtually all of those works
took the position

00:06:45.060 --> 00:06:48.638
that the Nazis were really not so bad,

00:06:48.662 --> 00:06:51.746
and the Allies were really not so good.

00:06:51.770 --> 00:06:53.875
And the Jews, whatever happened to them,

00:06:53.899 --> 00:06:55.209
they sort of deserved it.

00:06:56.206 --> 00:06:57.697
He knew the documents,

00:06:57.721 --> 00:06:59.164
he knew the facts,

00:06:59.188 --> 00:07:02.360
but he somehow twisted them
to get this opinion.

00:07:03.016 --> 00:07:05.528
He hadn't always been a Holocaust denier,

00:07:05.552 --> 00:07:07.293
but in the late '80s,

00:07:07.317 --> 00:07:09.744
he embraced it with great vigor.

00:07:11.517 --> 00:07:15.422
The reason I laughed also
was this was a man

00:07:15.446 --> 00:07:17.380
who not only was a Holocaust denier,

00:07:17.404 --> 00:07:19.099
but seemed quite proud of it.

00:07:19.123 --> 00:07:20.747
Here was a man -- and I quote --

00:07:20.771 --> 00:07:24.465
who said, "I'm going to sink
the battleship Auschwitz."

00:07:25.345 --> 00:07:26.517
Here was a man

00:07:26.541 --> 00:07:30.561
who pointed to the number tattooed
on a survivor's arm and said,

00:07:31.716 --> 00:07:33.308
"How much money have you made

00:07:33.332 --> 00:07:36.732
from having that number
tattooed on your arm?"

00:07:37.549 --> 00:07:39.457
Here was a man who said,

00:07:39.481 --> 00:07:42.437
"More people died in Senator Kennedy's car

00:07:42.461 --> 00:07:43.773
at Chappaquiddick

00:07:43.797 --> 00:07:47.111
than died in gas chambers at Auschwitz."

00:07:47.135 --> 00:07:49.972
That's an American reference,
but you can look it up.

00:07:51.406 --> 00:07:54.420
This was not a man who seemed
at all ashamed or reticent

00:07:54.444 --> 00:07:56.513
about being a Holocaust denier.

00:07:57.136 --> 00:08:00.916
Now, lots of my academic
colleagues counseled me --

00:08:00.940 --> 00:08:02.846
"Eh, Deborah, just ignore it."

00:08:02.870 --> 00:08:06.458
When I explained you can't just
ignore a libel suit,

00:08:06.482 --> 00:08:09.264
they said, "Who's going to
believe him anyway?"

00:08:09.783 --> 00:08:11.863
But here was the problem:

00:08:11.887 --> 00:08:17.195
British law put the onus,
put the burden of proof on me

00:08:17.219 --> 00:08:19.901
to prove the truth of what I said,

00:08:19.925 --> 00:08:22.688
in contrast to as it would have
been in the United States

00:08:22.712 --> 00:08:24.216
and in many other countries:

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:27.246
on him to prove the falsehood.

00:08:27.921 --> 00:08:29.382
What did that mean?

00:08:29.406 --> 00:08:32.782
That meant if I didn't fight,

00:08:32.806 --> 00:08:35.232
he would win by default.

00:08:35.791 --> 00:08:37.546
And if he won by default,

00:08:37.570 --> 00:08:40.211
he could then legitimately say,

00:08:40.235 --> 00:08:45.571
"My David Irving version of the Holocaust
is a legitimate version.

00:08:45.595 --> 00:08:47.779
Deborah Lipstadt was found
to have libeled me

00:08:47.803 --> 00:08:49.750
when she called me a Holocaust denier.

00:08:49.774 --> 00:08:54.202
Ipso facto, I, David Irving,
am not a Holocaust denier."

00:08:54.226 --> 00:08:55.938
And what is that version?

00:08:56.431 --> 00:08:59.427
There was no plan to murder the Jews,

00:08:59.451 --> 00:09:01.503
there were no gas chambers,

00:09:01.527 --> 00:09:03.383
there were no mass shootings,

00:09:03.407 --> 00:09:06.578
Hitler had nothing to do
with any suffering that went on,

00:09:06.602 --> 00:09:10.407
and the Jews have made this all up

00:09:10.431 --> 00:09:12.829
to get money from Germany

00:09:12.853 --> 00:09:14.560
and to get a state,

00:09:14.584 --> 00:09:17.961
and they've done it with the aid
and abettance of the Allies --

00:09:17.985 --> 00:09:21.450
they've planted the documents
and planted the evidence.

00:09:22.460 --> 00:09:24.840
I couldn't let that stand

00:09:24.864 --> 00:09:27.064
and ever face a survivor

00:09:27.823 --> 00:09:29.798
or a child of survivors.

00:09:29.822 --> 00:09:31.974
I couldn't let that stand

00:09:31.998 --> 00:09:36.249
and consider myself
a responsible historian.

00:09:37.187 --> 00:09:38.932
So we fought.

00:09:38.956 --> 00:09:41.238
And for those of you
who haven't seen "Denial,"

00:09:41.262 --> 00:09:42.421
spoiler alert:

00:09:42.445 --> 00:09:43.663
we won.

00:09:43.687 --> 00:09:44.982
(Laughter)

00:09:45.006 --> 00:09:47.573
(Applause)

00:09:51.988 --> 00:09:56.229
The judge found David Irving

00:09:56.253 --> 00:09:59.584
to be a liar,

00:09:59.608 --> 00:10:00.771
a racist,

00:10:00.795 --> 00:10:02.049
an anti-Semite.

00:10:02.073 --> 00:10:04.433
His view of history was tendentious,

00:10:04.457 --> 00:10:06.383
he lied, he distorted --

00:10:06.407 --> 00:10:09.050
and most importantly,

00:10:09.074 --> 00:10:11.187
he did it deliberately.

00:10:11.211 --> 00:10:15.350
We showed a pattern,
in over 25 different major instances.

00:10:15.374 --> 00:10:18.484
Not small things -- many of us
in this audience write books,

00:10:18.508 --> 00:10:19.693
are writing books;

00:10:19.717 --> 00:10:23.183
we always make mistakes, that's why
we're glad to have second editions:

00:10:23.207 --> 00:10:24.393
correct the mistakes.

00:10:24.417 --> 00:10:25.567
(Laughter)

00:10:26.634 --> 00:10:29.770
But these always moved
in the same direction:

00:10:30.618 --> 00:10:32.829
blame the Jews,

00:10:32.853 --> 00:10:35.028
exonerate the Nazis.

00:10:35.700 --> 00:10:37.284
But how did we win?

00:10:38.196 --> 00:10:43.576
What we did is follow his footnotes
back to his sources.

00:10:44.190 --> 00:10:45.973
And what did we find?

00:10:45.997 --> 00:10:47.476
Not in most cases,

00:10:47.500 --> 00:10:49.468
and not in the preponderance of cases,

00:10:49.492 --> 00:10:53.803
but in every single instance where
he made some reference to the Holocaust,

00:10:53.827 --> 00:10:58.069
that his supposed evidence was distorted,

00:10:58.093 --> 00:10:59.513
half-truth,

00:10:59.537 --> 00:11:00.871
date-changed,

00:11:00.895 --> 00:11:03.082
sequence-changed,

00:11:03.106 --> 00:11:05.230
someone put at a meeting who wasn't there.

00:11:05.254 --> 00:11:08.015
In other words,
he didn't have the evidence.

00:11:08.039 --> 00:11:10.148
His evidence didn't prove it.

00:11:10.172 --> 00:11:12.831
We didn't prove what happened.

00:11:13.628 --> 00:11:16.127
We proved that what he said happened --

00:11:16.151 --> 00:11:19.011
and by extension, all deniers,
because he either quotes them

00:11:19.035 --> 00:11:21.506
or they get their arguments from him --

00:11:21.530 --> 00:11:22.776
is not true.

00:11:22.800 --> 00:11:23.989
What they claim --

00:11:24.013 --> 00:11:26.635
they don't have the evidence to prove it.

00:11:28.609 --> 00:11:33.353
So why is my story
more than just the story

00:11:33.377 --> 00:11:37.184
of a quirky, long,
six-year, difficult lawsuit,

00:11:37.208 --> 00:11:42.197
an American professor
being dragged into a courtroom

00:11:42.221 --> 00:11:45.265
by a man that the court
declared in its judgment

00:11:45.289 --> 00:11:47.539
was a neo-Nazi polemicist?

00:11:47.563 --> 00:11:49.346
What message does it have?

00:11:49.800 --> 00:11:52.773
I think in the context
of the question of truth,

00:11:52.797 --> 00:11:55.259
it has a very significant message.

00:11:55.283 --> 00:11:57.068
Because today,

00:11:57.092 --> 00:11:58.758
as we well know,

00:11:58.782 --> 00:12:02.898
truth and facts are under assault.

00:12:03.702 --> 00:12:06.954
Social media, for all
the gifts it has given us,

00:12:06.978 --> 00:12:12.559
has also allowed the difference
between facts -- established facts --

00:12:12.583 --> 00:12:14.340
and lies

00:12:14.364 --> 00:12:15.762
to be flattened.

00:12:16.990 --> 00:12:18.500
Third of all:

00:12:18.524 --> 00:12:19.995
extremism.

00:12:20.987 --> 00:12:24.564
You may not see Ku Klux Klan robes,

00:12:24.588 --> 00:12:26.659
you may not see burning crosses,

00:12:26.683 --> 00:12:31.002
you may not even hear outright
white supremacist language.

00:12:31.026 --> 00:12:35.932
It may go by names: "alt-right,"
"National Front" -- pick your names.

00:12:35.956 --> 00:12:41.791
But underneath, it's that same extremism
that I found in Holocaust denial

00:12:41.815 --> 00:12:45.209
parading as rational discourse.

00:12:47.134 --> 00:12:52.351
We live in an age
where truth is on the defensive.

00:12:52.375 --> 00:12:54.859
I'm reminded of a New Yorker cartoon.

00:12:54.883 --> 00:12:57.403
A quiz show recently appeared
in "The New Yorker"

00:12:57.427 --> 00:13:00.649
where the host of the quiz show
is saying to one of the contestants,

00:13:00.673 --> 00:13:02.982
"Yes, ma'am, you had the right answer.

00:13:03.006 --> 00:13:05.499
But your opponent yelled
more loudly than you did,

00:13:05.523 --> 00:13:07.048
so he gets the point."

00:13:08.228 --> 00:13:09.735
What can we do?

00:13:10.557 --> 00:13:11.934
First of all,

00:13:11.958 --> 00:13:17.389
we cannot be beguiled
by rational appearances.

00:13:17.413 --> 00:13:19.182
We've got to look underneath,

00:13:19.206 --> 00:13:22.007
and we will find there the extremism.

00:13:22.991 --> 00:13:24.977
Second of all,

00:13:25.001 --> 00:13:31.082
we must understand
that truth is not relative.

00:13:33.137 --> 00:13:34.601
Number three,

00:13:34.625 --> 00:13:38.314
we must go on the offensive,

00:13:38.338 --> 00:13:40.111
not the defensive.

00:13:40.676 --> 00:13:43.283
When someone makes an outrageous claim,

00:13:43.307 --> 00:13:46.811
even though they may hold
one of the highest offices in the land,

00:13:46.835 --> 00:13:48.846
if not the world --

00:13:48.870 --> 00:13:50.380
we must say to them,

00:13:50.404 --> 00:13:52.370
"Where's the proof?

00:13:52.394 --> 00:13:54.531
Where's the evidence?"

00:13:54.555 --> 00:13:57.482
We must hold their feet to the fire.

00:13:57.506 --> 00:14:02.112
We must not treat it as if their lies
are the same as the facts.

00:14:03.395 --> 00:14:06.935
And as I said earlier,
truth is not relative.

00:14:06.959 --> 00:14:09.815
Many of us have grown up
in the world of the academy

00:14:09.839 --> 00:14:11.580
and enlightened liberal thought,

00:14:11.604 --> 00:14:14.565
where we're taught
everything is open to debate.

00:14:15.164 --> 00:14:17.178
But that's not the case.

00:14:17.202 --> 00:14:20.644
There are certain things that are true.

00:14:21.192 --> 00:14:24.212
There are indisputable facts --

00:14:24.236 --> 00:14:25.926
objective truths.

00:14:26.519 --> 00:14:31.336
Galileo taught it to us centuries ago.

00:14:31.360 --> 00:14:36.027
Even after being forced
to recant by the Vatican

00:14:36.051 --> 00:14:38.624
that the Earth moved around the Sun,

00:14:38.648 --> 00:14:39.802
he came out,

00:14:39.826 --> 00:14:42.136
and what is he reported to have said?

00:14:42.160 --> 00:14:45.982
"And yet, it still moves."

00:14:47.342 --> 00:14:50.182
The Earth is not flat.

00:14:50.206 --> 00:14:52.496
The climate is changing.

00:14:53.387 --> 00:14:55.655
Elvis is not alive.

00:14:55.679 --> 00:14:57.214
(Laughter)

00:14:57.238 --> 00:14:59.554
(Applause)

00:14:59.578 --> 00:15:01.879
And most importantly,

00:15:01.903 --> 00:15:06.552
truth and fact are under assault.

00:15:07.289 --> 00:15:08.899
The job ahead of us,

00:15:08.923 --> 00:15:10.126
the task ahead of us,

00:15:10.150 --> 00:15:11.744
the challenge ahead of us

00:15:11.768 --> 00:15:13.002
is great.

00:15:13.747 --> 00:15:16.384
The time to fight is short.

00:15:17.241 --> 00:15:20.084
We must act now.

00:15:20.929 --> 00:15:24.174
Later will be too late.

00:15:24.198 --> 00:15:25.460
Thank you very much.

00:15:25.484 --> 00:15:29.530
(Applause)

